  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to byacc</title>

    <para>
      The byacc package contains an implementation of <command>yacc</command>
      originating from BSD.
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download (HTTP): <ulink url="&byacc-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of byacc</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>byacc</application> by executing the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr      \
            --program-prefix=b \
            --with-manpage-format=formatted &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now as the &root; user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

